               <msContents>
                  <summary>Psalter, ዳዊት፡, Angels Praise Her, ይዌድስዋ፡ መላእክት፡ ለማርያም፡</summary>
                    <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="160v" facs="007">Fols 1r–160v</locus><title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2701Dawit">Psalter</title>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                    <note>starting at the end of Psalm 2</note>
                    <note><ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2000Mazmur#Ps118Spiritual"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: LIT2000Mazmur#Ps118Spiritual</span></ref> only for the letter aleph</note>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
